title: Incinerator Core Supporter Pack
description: The Incinerator Core Supporter Pack contains five Armour Sets, five Wings, five Apparition Portal Effects, five Weapon Effects, three Weapon Skins, a Helmet Attachment, Path of Exile Signed Tarot Cards, Zana or Exalted Orb or Path of Exile Logo Hoodie, Zana or Exalted Orb or Path of Exile Logo T-Shirt, five Social Frames, five Forum Titles, five Badges and 4800 points.
